  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 7th level, you learn to truly see into the world of your Spirit, attaining a new level of understanding of that which lies around you. You gain 15 feet of true sight, which doubles while wielding your Ego Weapon. You also gain advantage on checks to locate creatures within the range of this sight, and can add your Charisma modifier to Perception and Investigation checks you make.</p><p></p><p></p>",
